data.title: The Most Memorable Moments from the Black Cat 20th Anniversary Shows
data.meta_description: This weekend the Black Cat invited old D.C. music stalwarts and promising new bands to celebrate the club's 20th anniversary. Across the board, the performances from the weekend were spirited and the joy and reverence for the space, genuine. However, throughout the weekend-long party a few moments stood out.
